1
00:00:57,989 --> 00:01:00,965
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,965 --> 00:01:02,935
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:02,935 --> 00:01:06,957
(Chaosheng Comes Late at Night)

4
00:01:07,008 --> 00:01:09,486
(Zhanchun Pavilion, Gu Mansion)

5
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,040
Master.

6
00:01:20,783 --> 00:01:22,798
(Gu Jiang, head of the Gu family)

7
00:01:25,518 --> 00:01:27,200
(Heaven)

8
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:38,560
(During this period, I disguised myself
and investigated beside General Shen.)

9
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,000
(He didn't commit treason.)

10
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:45,560
(He's an upright and incorruptible man.)

11
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:48,519
(He already caught the one
who framed him in Suzhou.)

12
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:50,439
(He will return soon.)

13
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,280
You've done well.

14
00:01:56,760 --> 00:02:02,480
Since General Shen
is not involved in that matter,

15
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:05,159
his name is cleared.

16
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,919
I promised

17
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:14,039
to hand Xuanji Pavilion over to you
after your marriage to Zhaoxi.

18
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:16,240
Now, he...

19
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:22,439
Heaven will protect Master Zhaoxi.

20
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,960
I heard about the thing a few days ago.

21
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:28,599
I've already made Chaosheng
accept his punishment.

22
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,479
I'm sorry about that.

23
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:35,800
I'll await Master Zhaoxi's safe return.

24
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,680
(Heaven)
Go and report back.

25
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:43,960
Yes.

26
00:02:56,992 --> 00:02:59,971
(Xuanji Pavilion)

27
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:34,719
(19 years ago, Gu Jiang
went mad during a visit.)

28
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:37,120
(He killed the family
of Left Chancellor Qin Yuheng.)

29
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:40,719
(This Heaven mission remains
unresolved in the Shadow Pavilion.)

30
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:46,599
(Gu Jiang brought back
Qin Yuheng's baby daughter, Qin Xiang,)

31
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,199
(kept her in Xuanji Pavilion)

32
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,120
(and named her Yuluo.)

33
00:04:15,616 --> 00:04:17,651
(Xuan Wu, Xuan Unit of Xuanji Pavilion)

34
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:25,879
I thought I'd be congratulating
the new Pavilion Master.

35
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,600
Sorry to disappoint you.

36
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:39,279
I didn't expect you to be interested
in the position of Pavilion Master.

37
00:04:54,238 --> 00:04:58,071
(Earth)

38
00:05:10,464 --> 00:05:14,592
(Xuanji Pavilion)

39
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:21,199
Don't worry. I'm not that impatient.

40
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,319
I'm waiting for your action.

41
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,879
What do you truly want, Master?

42
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:30,600
I dare not guess your mind.

43
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,839
But over all these years,

44
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,240
you've never wanted for anything.

45
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:38,279
Why this obsession now?

46
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:45,959
The secret scrolls within the pavilion
are only accessible to Pavilion Masters.

47
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:49,480
Does your desire to become
the Xuanji Pavilion Master

48
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:53,839
have something to do with
the anonymous letter you often read?

49
00:06:10,439 --> 00:06:12,160
(The contents of that secret letter)

50
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:15,240
(are connected
to Xuanji Pavilion's Heaven mission.)

51
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,279
(To know if the thing
back then is true,)

52
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:22,040
(I need to wait.)

53
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:32,079
I'd like to share your burdens, Master.

54
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:36,079
You've already shared many.

55
00:06:38,432 --> 00:06:40,320
(Fufeng Pavilion, Gu Mansion)

56
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,199
Do you recognize what these are?

57
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,279
How would I recognize
these women's stuff?

58
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:02,680
Actually, you'll need all of them.

59
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:08,759
I have repaid the money you owed

60
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,279
at Zuixian Building.

61
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:14,160
I've also sent people
to find your relatives in the city.

62
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:20,560
In your name, I gifted them 100 taels
of gold and arranged careful protection.

63
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,600
Do you have any other wishes?

64
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:30,040
He wouldn't look at me the way you do.

65
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:35,120
How would he look?

66
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,759
This is Master Zhaoxi.

67
00:07:52,064 --> 00:07:55,744
(Gu Zhaoxi, third young master
of the Gu family)

68
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:58,779
♪Slowly turning into love♪

69
00:08:00,064 --> 00:08:04,846
♪But why is there a sigh in your eyes♪

70
00:08:06,688 --> 00:08:10,224
♪Flowers bloom and you'll return♪

71
00:08:10,976 --> 00:08:13,696
♪We're bound to meet♪

72
00:08:14,592 --> 00:08:18,749
♪My heart has never been far away♪

73
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,959
Lady, feel free.

74
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:25,839
Though we've lived
in the same mansion, we've never met.

75
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,120
I have long heard of you.

76
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,279
Regarding our marriage,

77
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:34,720
since Father has arranged it,
there must be a reason.

78
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:39,039
But I'm frail and chronically ill.

79
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,879
If you are unwilling,
I will persuade Father

80
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,000
to decline this marriage.

81
00:08:55,478 --> 00:08:59,072
♪Stroke by stroke, bit by bit♪

82
00:08:59,697 --> 00:09:02,743
♪Like rain seeping into the earth♪

83
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:08,561
♪Love blooms from the void♪

84
00:09:10,208 --> 00:09:13,933
♪I'll accompany you to whatever end♪

85
00:09:14,752 --> 00:09:17,777
♪Helplessly falling for you♪

86
00:09:18,432 --> 00:09:22,464
♪You are my only one♪

87
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:27,138
♪Writing a love poem for you♪

88
00:09:27,890 --> 00:09:30,810
♪Writing our unfinished story♪

89
00:09:31,456 --> 00:09:37,118
♪Your name fills every line♪

90
00:09:38,496 --> 00:09:41,802
♪Let time rush by♪

91
00:09:42,304 --> 00:09:45,632
♪Love so deep, I care not for the cost♪

92
00:09:45,856 --> 00:09:52,320
♪This moment weaves eternity♪

93
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,200
Master, we should leave.

94
00:09:57,632 --> 00:10:00,657
♪Writing our unfinished story♪

95
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:07,313
♪Countless stars reflect your face♪

96
00:10:08,629 --> 00:10:12,288
♪Let time rush by♪

97
00:10:12,288 --> 00:10:15,995
♪Love so deep, I care not for the cost♪

98
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:20,240
Master Zhaoxi,

99
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:22,000
I'm willing.

100
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:30,679
♪A love poem awaits our rediscovery♪

101
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,600
When you fully recover,

102
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,480
we can finish this game together.

103
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:41,919
I shall await your return.

104
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:55,120
(He must not find out that Gu Zhaoxi
and I have only met once.)

105
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:02,960
My husband is the gentlest, most humble,
and kindest man in the world to me.

106
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,399
He indulges me in everything.

107
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,000
Whether I want frost flowers
atop the mountain

108
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,200
or fireflies on a summer night,

109
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:13,000
he would seek them out for me.

110
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:16,720
If I get up early,
he prepares congee for me.

111
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:20,039
If I return late,
he lights a lamp and waits for me.

112
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:23,799
We share perfect harmony
and play chess in our leisure.

113
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:27,240
Knowing I fear the cold,
he often warms my hands with his.

114
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:32,559
He's delighted whenever he sees me.

115
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,279
When he smiles,

116
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,960
it's like a clear breeze
and bright moon, pure and untainted.

117
00:11:53,279 --> 00:11:57,960
From now on,
you are my husband, Gu Zhaoxi.

118
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:01,480
(Can two people truly be
so identical in this world?)

119
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,759
(Or...)

120
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,640
The Gu family specializes in disguise.

121
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,679
They replaced your coachman
and tried to assassinate you.

122
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:10,720
They even created a face
identical to yours at their place.

123
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:14,080
I wonder what they are plotting.

124
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,320
Investigate them,

125
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,120
and then we'll know.

126
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:26,759
I will briefly tell you some
of his habits and preferences.

127
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:32,200
Tomorrow, we can announce
the news of your return.

128
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:35,360
Your voice is a problem.

129
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,039
However,

130
00:12:38,759 --> 00:12:40,399
we can use your injury as an excuse

131
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:42,679
to avoid guests while you adapt.

132
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:46,159
As for the sword wound on your body,

133
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:50,519
it can also serve as the reason
for your delayed return.

134
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,159
Let me see your sword wound.

135
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,759
A minor injury.

136
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:04,919
It's already been dressed.

137
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,200
You're so easily flustered.

138
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:13,200
How will you handle
pretending to be my husband?

139
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:18,679
Master Chaosheng, my master
is bathing. You cannot enter.

140
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:21,519
What? A Xuanji Pavilion's death guard
is fighting against me?

141
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:32,639
Such deep affection between you two.

142
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,639
It makes me look like the villain,

143
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:38,960
breaking up you couple
and ruining our brotherhood.

144
00:13:40,279 --> 00:13:41,960
You have your reasons.

145
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:45,480
But Zhaoxi and I vowed
to be together long ago.

146
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:48,320
So I refuse to believe
he would abandon me.

147
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:53,000
I have heard something interesting.

148
00:13:53,559 --> 00:13:56,559
My martial-obsessed fourth brother,
who once studied at the Xuanji Pavilion,

149
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,320
seems quite close to you as well.

150
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,320
What do you mean by that?

151
00:14:06,519 --> 00:14:09,279
Although we both come
from the Xuanji Pavilion,

152
00:14:09,639 --> 00:14:11,440
we merely have a master-servant bond.

153
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:14,120
How can you say we are close?

154
00:14:17,799 --> 00:14:18,600
Master and servant?

155
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,720
So you know your place?

156
00:14:23,279 --> 00:14:24,480
But I heard

157
00:14:25,519 --> 00:14:27,960
he wrote to Father
requesting to marry you?

158
00:14:40,879 --> 00:14:44,600
I think you wouldn't believe
such baseless rumors.

159
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:48,080
The dead Zhaoxi
and the martial-obsessed fourth brother.

160
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,840
Instead of focusing
your efforts on them,

161
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:55,120
if you want the Xuanji Pavilion

162
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,480
or to become master of the Gu family,

163
00:14:58,919 --> 00:15:00,200
curry favor with me.

164
00:15:11,159 --> 00:15:11,960
Who's there?

165
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,279
Just the wind.

166
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:52,039
What are you worried about?
Eavesdroppers?

167
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:55,919
Worried?

168
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:59,360
I only worry your loyalty to Zhaoxi
isn't as unwavering as you claim.

169
00:15:59,879 --> 00:16:00,960
Hiding a man in your room?

170
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:04,039
I'm afraid you'll be disappointed.

171
00:16:05,559 --> 00:16:06,559
It's getting late.

172
00:16:07,279 --> 00:16:08,519
Please leave.

173
00:16:14,759 --> 00:16:15,559
Oh,

174
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:18,279
don't forget what I just said.

175
00:16:19,039 --> 00:16:20,360
If you change your mind someday,

176
00:16:21,799 --> 00:16:23,000
you are welcome to come to me.

177
00:16:31,759 --> 00:16:32,559
Come out.

178
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,240
Dear.

179
00:16:55,799 --> 00:16:58,440
I didn't realize my husband
is such an expert at hiding.

180
00:16:58,759 --> 00:16:59,960
That was dangerous just now.

181
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:03,000
I had to protect your reputation.

182
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,119
Is it safe now?

183
00:17:07,519 --> 00:17:08,319
Sure.

184
00:17:09,559 --> 00:17:11,400
Thank you.

185
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:23,839
If you don't come out, I'm going in.

186
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:00,519
You're so careless.

187
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:04,160
I thought you liked this kind of fun.

188
00:18:05,599 --> 00:18:06,519
Put me down.

189
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,799
Don't let it happen again.

190
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:26,240
I'm afraid I might lose control
and accidentally hurt you.

191
00:18:34,079 --> 00:18:36,200
Four hours, not a moment less.

192
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:25,279
(If Gu Zhaoxi harbors ill intent,
he's bound to leave traces.)

193
00:19:27,119 --> 00:19:28,480
(If he intends to mimic me,)

194
00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:31,960
(is there proof of his gathering details
about my habits and preferences)

195
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:37,119
(or a portrait of his true face?)

196
00:20:18,373 --> 00:20:23,436
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

197
00:20:23,973 --> 00:20:29,294
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

198
00:20:29,861 --> 00:20:36,489
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

199
00:20:36,489 --> 00:20:41,253
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

200
00:20:41,253 --> 00:20:43,589
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

201
00:20:43,589 --> 00:20:50,289
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

202
00:20:50,289 --> 00:20:57,061
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

203
00:20:57,061 --> 00:21:04,197
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

204
00:21:04,197 --> 00:21:08,581
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

205
00:21:08,581 --> 00:21:11,205
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

206
00:21:11,205 --> 00:21:17,839
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

207
00:21:17,839 --> 00:21:24,389
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

208
00:21:24,389 --> 00:21:31,513
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

209
00:21:31,603 --> 00:21:35,973
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

210
00:21:35,973 --> 00:21:38,681
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

211
00:21:38,681 --> 00:21:44,581
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

212
00:21:45,221 --> 00:21:51,209
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

